rows.label: tlk45600551_04_msg0001
rows.name:
The Superbian Divine Beast may not be in
the greatest of shape, but at least
our economy is thriving.

rows.label: tlk45600551_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Business around here is better than
I've ever seen it before.

rows.label: tlk45600551_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Apparently we're collaborating
with other nations, even Invidia,
to make entirely new products.

rows.label: tlk45600551_04_msg0004
rows.name:
I'd considered the idea of that sort
of collaboration before, but I never
thought it would become a reality.

rows.label: tlk45600551_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Maybe the promise of profits is all it
takes for our nations to get along, haha!
